<H3> <TI>   Kazan Hosts Conference of Regional Law Enforcement Officers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kazan Hosts Conference of Regional Law Enforcement Officers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM3103134394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 31 Mar 94 
First Edition p 6 </F>

