<H3> <TI>   Rio Traffickers Extending Operations to Baixada Fluminense </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rio Traffickers Extending Operations to Baixada Fluminense </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0288B Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 8 
Mar 94 p 6--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

