<H3> <TI>   Arrested Trafficker Reveals New Alliance in Rio </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Arrested Trafficker Reveals New Alliance in Rio </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0288A Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 8 
Mar 94 p 16--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

