<H3> <TI>   New Security Forces To Tackle Drug Problem in Tskhinvali </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Security Forces To Tackle Drug Problem in Tskhinvali </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0804081494 Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA in Russian 1 Apr 94 
p 4 </F>

