<H3> <TI>   Border Troops Seize Nearly 3 Kg of Heroin </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Border Troops Seize Nearly 3 Kg of Heroin </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0804113794 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 1000 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0804113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] As the Ukrainian Border Troops press service has 
reported today, the last day on the Ukrainian-Moldovan border 
was quite tense. Soldiers of the Kotiv Border Control Squad 
prevented an attempted contraband of 10 tonnes of diesel fuel to 
Moldova, and at [words indistinct] Border Troops soldiers 
detained a truck with 20 tonnes of coal which Moldovan citizens 
attempted to transport to Moldova. Attempts to smuggle firearms 
and drugs through our borders also continue. For example, a 
Nagan gun and ammunition for it were found with a Kazakhstani 
citizen, and in Sumy Oblast, while searching the Kiev-Moscow 
train, Border Troops soldiers uncovered almost 3 kg of heroin. 
All the cases are currently under investigation. 

</TEXT>

