<H3> <TI>   Deputies Comment on Report, Need for U.S. Assistance </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputies Comment on Report, Need for U.S. Assistance </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA0604194894 Managua Sistema Nacional de Television Network 
