extensive measures to control narcotics, not only in the region 
but also globally. Tehran's investment in the matter is of the 
highest level. 
  The U.S. assistant secretary of state claimed last Monday 
that the Islamic Republic of Iran is taking no measures to fight 
narcotics smuggling. 

