  [Text] Jeddah, April 15, SPA -- The Ministry of the 
Interior issued a statement saying that Bashir Ahmad Bashir 
Karkahsah, a Syrian national, was beheaded here on Friday for 
smuggling hashish into the kingdom. The statement said the 
